  "description": {
    "zh": "好了，我们现在继续。西方手枪都很酷，但我们自己的呢？我们 mostly 是较老的武器，追溯到苏联时代，但 newer ones 有点缺乏模块化。你在这里处于轻微的劣势，我的哥们，你得玩得聪明点。\n\n这些武器使用的弹药很糟糕，瞄准无护甲区域或直接爆头是你唯一的选择，我是认真的。明白？",
    "en": "Alright then, we're moving on now. Western pistols are all cool and all but what about ours? We got mostly older weapons, back from the soviet times, but the newer ones kinda lack the modularity. You're at a slight disadvantage here my man, you gotta play this smart.\n\nThese weapons use terrible ammunition, going for unarmored areas or straight for the head is your only option here, and I mean it. Copy?."
  },
